      <div>
        <p><em>#1 of 6 of the series Documenting Components:<br /></em><strong>Overview </strong>| <a href="https://medium.com/eightshapes-llc/documenting-component-introductions-fe5b04287284" target="_blank">Intros</a> | <a href="https://medium.com/eightshapes-llc/component-examples-9c4b3bb3b308" target="_blank">Examples</a> | <a href="https://medium.com/eightshapes-llc/component-design-guidelines-eca706100e7c" target="_blank">Design</a> | Code | Authoring</p>
